Dialogue: 0.0:17:19.80.0:17:26.41.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  I treated you bad  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:17:26.48.0:17:32.02.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  And wrong. my dear. and. girl. since  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:17:32.08.0:17:37.09.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Since you went away  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:17:37.15.0:17:41.82.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Don't you know I sit around  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:17:41.89.0:17:46.16.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  With my head hanging down  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:17:46.23.0:17:52.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  And I wonder who's loving you  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:17:53.17.0:17:57.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  I. I. I. I...  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:17:58.94.0:18:00.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Let me tell you something. son.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:18:01.88.0:18:04.45.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I've been doing this a long time.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:04.51.0:18:07.45.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I've never heard a voice quite like yours.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:07.52.0:18:10.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You sang that song better than Smokey himself.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:10.95.0:18:12.12.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Really?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:13.62.0:18:14.62.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You're special.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:16.03.0:18:17.43.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You have something to say.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:18.43.0:18:20.86.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..That's rare. Michael.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:20.93.0:18:22.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. this is the fader. Come on. try it.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:22.97.0:18:25.84.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Move it up. This fader goes up and down
Dialogue: 0.0:18:25.90.0:18:27.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- and it sets the levels...  - Wow.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:27.20.0:18:28.54.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..to the volume.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:28.61.0:18:31.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It can make your voice sound... ...louder...
Dialogue: 0.0:18:31.14.0:18:32.41.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0.....or softer.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:32.47.0:18:33.84.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- All right?  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:33.91.0:18:36.24.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And these knobs up here. that's for your EQ.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:36.31.0:18:37.41.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What's EQ?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:37.48.0:18:39.28.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Equalization.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:39.35.0:18:40.65.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You see. when we record.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:40.72.0:18:42.15.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..we split things up in track. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:42.22.0:18:44.15.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Excuse me. uh... Time to go. Michael.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:44.22.0:18:45.66.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Mr. Gordy's a very busy man.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:45.72.0:18:47.52.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm sure you've taken up enough of his time.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:50.83.0:18:52.10.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Go ahead on. Michael.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:52.16.0:18:54.40.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I can show you this stuff some other time. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:54.46.0:18:57.10.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Okay. Mr. Gordy. Thank you.  - All right. Mm-hmm.
