Dialogue: 0.0:19:44.48.0:19:46.28.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Come on and love me just a little bit...  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:19:46.35.0:19:48.38.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..All right. so. how old are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:48.45.0:19:49.45.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Ten.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:49.52.0:19:51.75.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. you're not ten. You're eight.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:51.82.0:19:53.09.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Come on. come on. come on  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:19:53.16.0:19:54.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Let me show you what it's all about  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:19:54.36.0:19:56.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Reading. writing. arithmetic  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:19:56.39.0:19:58.66.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..In this business. you can make up just about anything.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:58.73.0:19:59.96.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..especially your age.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:00.03.0:20:01.80.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Your education ain't complete  ♫{\i0}
