Dialogue: 0.0:20:25.25.0:20:27.26.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Michael! How old are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:27.32.0:20:29.26.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- {\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Sing a simple melody  ♫{\i0}{\c}  - {\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Do-Re-Mi  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:20:29.32.0:20:31.43.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  A. B. C. that's how easy...  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:20:31.49.0:20:33.16.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm. uh. I'm eight. sir.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:39.37.0:20:41.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Sit down. girl  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:20:41.40.0:20:44.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  I think I love ya  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:20:44.17.0:20:48.44.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  No. get up. girl. show me what you can do  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:20:48.51.0:20:50.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Shake it. shake it. baby  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:20:50.25.0:20:53.02.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Come on now. shake it. shake it. baby  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:20:57.69.0:21:00.19.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Ooh-ooh. A. B. C. baby  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:21:00.26.0:21:02.79.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Nah nah. Do-Re-Mi. baby  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:21:02.86.0:21:06.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Ow! That's how easy love can be  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:21:11.43.0:21:14.24.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I have been reading about the Serengeti.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:14.30.0:21:18.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Learning about all different types of lions. tigers.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:19.04.0:21:22.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..monkeys. giraffes.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:22.25.0:21:25.72.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..One day. you and I will have more friends to play with.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:25.78.0:21:27.88.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Wouldn't that be fun?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:27.95.0:21:30.09.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Look at this picture. You like it?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:32.96.0:21:34.96.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Come on. Michael. Joseph wants you.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:37.13.0:21:39.93.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And make sure you put your rat in the cage this time.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:40.00.0:21:41.63.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:43.73.0:21:44.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Come on now.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:47.64.0:21:48.94.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Meet Bill Bray.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:49.01.0:21:51.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..He's your new head of security. all right?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:51.21.0:21:52.64.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Now. he's gonna be around a lot.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:53.51.0:21:54.94.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Make sure you mind him.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:56.51.0:21:58.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Nice to meet you. Mr. Bray.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:58.58.0:22:00.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's very nice to meet you. too. young man.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:00.65.0:22:01.82.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You can call me Bill. okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:02.65.0:22:03.75.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay. Bill.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:04.59.0:22:05.66.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..All right.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:08.29.0:22:10.36.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Guard him with your life.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:11.79.0:22:15.03.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Michael! You're missing the best part.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:39.62.0:22:41.12.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And llamas have three stomachs.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:41.19.0:22:42.66.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..so they can digest their food
Dialogue: 0.0:22:42.73.0:22:44.56.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..because all they eat is vegetables.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:44.63.0:22:46.93.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And they're really smart. very intelligent creatures.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:47.00.0:22:50.00.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And best of all. they never ever bite.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:50.07.0:22:51.77.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..That's what you said about the rats.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:51.83.0:22:53.77.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. really. Llamas never bite.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:53.84.0:22:56.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..They only spit when they're agitated.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:56.34.0:22:57.61.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..So. you want me to bring some
Dialogue: 0.0:22:57.67.0:23:00.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..spitting. agitated animal into my house?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:00.24.0:23:02.28.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..He'll live outside. Come on. please.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:02.35.0:23:03.75.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Please say yes.  - No.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:03.81.0:23:06.78.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- I'll look after him.  - Absolutely not. Michael.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:06.85.0:23:08.78.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Mother has enough things to worry about.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:08.85.0:23:10.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And you don't need another pet.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:10.39.0:23:11.92.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..They're not my pets.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:11.99.0:23:13.59.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..They're my friends.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:17.36.0:23:19.00.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well...
Dialogue: 0.0:23:22.00.0:23:24.43.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I do understand that.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:24.50.0:23:26.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..But don't you want to meet real friends.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:26.34.0:23:28.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..like. kids your own age?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:29.91.0:23:31.74.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I would like that for you.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:33.44.0:23:37.15.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I do sometimes. but I'm not like the other kids.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:37.21.0:23:40.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..They don't treat me like a real person.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:40.55.0:23:42.45.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And all they want to do is stare
Dialogue: 0.0:23:42.52.0:23:44.12.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and take pictures of me.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:51.76.0:23:54.06.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. you look at me. Michael.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:55.93.0:23:59.67.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I knew you were different the moment you were born.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:59.74.0:24:02.17.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I knew you were different from your brothers.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:02.24.0:24:04.47.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and that's okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:04.54.0:24:07.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You have a very special light.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:08.24.0:24:10.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And you know what Jehovah says.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:10.31.0:24:13.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..He says. "Let your light shine
Dialogue: 0.0:24:13.25.0:24:15.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0.."unto the world."
Dialogue: 0.0:24:15.65.0:24:17.65.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Now. you let your light shine.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:18.99.0:24:20.82.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:22.56.0:24:24.09.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:24.16.0:24:27.23.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Don't you ever let anyone take that away from you.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:28.63.0:24:30.47.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Not even yourself.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:33.30.0:24:34.54.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Come here.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:40.58.0:24:42.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}The next song we're gonna do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:24:42.58.0:24:45.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}is one of our favorites. You guys ready?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:24:52.09.0:24:58.09.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  You and I must make a pact  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:24:58.16.0:25:03.83.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  We must bring salvation back  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:25:05.13.0:25:09.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Where there is love  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:25:09.34.0:25:12.78.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- {\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  I'll be there  ♫{\i0}{\c}  - {\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  I'll be there  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:25:16.38.0:25:20.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  I'll be there to protect you  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:25:20.58.0:25:21.82.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Yeah. baby  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:25:21.88.0:25:24.22.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  With an unselfish love  ♫{\i0}
