Dialogue: 0.0:34:37.41.0:34:38.68.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Don't stop 'til you get enough  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:34:38.74.0:34:40.21.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Keep on with the force. don't stop  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:34:40.28.0:34:42.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Go crazy. baby  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:34:43.28.0:34:44.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Keep on  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:34:44.55.0:34:46.28.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Don't stop 'til you get enough  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:34:46.35.0:34:48.55.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Keep on. darling  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:34:48.62.0:34:51.12.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Ah. ah. now  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:34:57.89.0:34:59.46.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Mmm. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:08.37.0:35:10.21.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's almost here. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:12.54.0:35:14.54.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- What does he have going on?  - What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:14.61.0:35:15.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's a surprise.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:16.05.0:35:18.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. is it a car? Did you get a damn Ferrari. Michael?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:19.05.0:35:20.22.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Mike. I'm going back to bed.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:20.28.0:35:23.15.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Marlon. Tito. don't wake your father up.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:25.22.0:35:26.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..La Toya.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:27.46.0:35:28.76.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Do you know about this?  - Mm-mm.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:28.83.0:35:29.86.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What's going on?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:29.93.0:35:31.43.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Rockin' robin  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:35:32.33.0:35:33.43.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Blow. rockin' robin...  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:35:34.93.0:35:37.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  'Cause we're really gonna rock tonight  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:35:37.97.0:35:39.00.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Every little swallow. every chickadee...  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:35:39.07.0:35:40.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What you got going on. Mike?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:41.80.0:35:43.57.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You'll see.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:43.64.0:35:46.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  The wise old owl. the big black crow  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:35:46.17.0:35:49.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Flappin' their wings singin' "Go. bird. go"  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:36:07.53.0:36:09.93.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. wow.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:12.97.0:36:14.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:21.11.0:36:22.38.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Go on.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:22.44.0:36:24.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Aw. it's okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:35.02.0:36:37.66.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I want you to meet my new friend. Bubbles.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:37.73.0:36:39.60.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:39.66.0:36:42.23.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I rescued him from this awful place
Dialogue: 0.0:36:42.30.0:36:44.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..where they do testing on animals.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:45.03.0:36:47.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Welcome to the family.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:47.34.0:36:50.31.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Michael. you do know that chimps are wild animals
Dialogue: 0.0:36:50.37.0:36:53.74.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..that don't belong in a house in Encino.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:53.81.0:36:56.24.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Mother. I'll take good care of him.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:56.31.0:36:57.38.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I will. I promise.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:58.21.0:36:59.31.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Does he bite?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:59.38.0:37:01.42.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. no. No. he's sweet.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:02.52.0:37:04.62.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..But. you know. chimps...
Dialogue: 0.0:37:04.69.0:37:05.79.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..are sensitive. though. you know.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:05.86.0:37:08.83.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..to certain sounds and people.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:08.89.0:37:11.03.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You know. they either hide or they attack.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:21.77.0:37:23.61.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's okay. Bubbles. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:24.27.0:37:25.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You're safe now.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:28.61.0:37:30.28.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You want to make some music. huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:38.86.0:37:40.06.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..That's me.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:40.12.0:37:41.96.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I just released my new album.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:42.69.0:37:43.89.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Those are my demos.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:43.96.0:37:45.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Don't mess that up.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:47.30.0:37:50.20.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Here. I want to show you this. Look.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:52.94.0:37:54.04.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Look.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:54.90.0:37:56.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You see?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:59.14.0:38:00.81.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..This is Neverland.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:00.88.0:38:02.55.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I come here all the time.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:05.25.0:38:07.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's filled with magic.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:07.15.0:38:08.68.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..adventure.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:08.75.0:38:09.89.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..pirates.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:09.95.0:38:11.55.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Here. I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:13.06.0:38:15.06.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Look. the Lost Boys.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:20.73.0:38:23.23.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..This is my favorite page. It's Peter Pan.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:24.17.0:38:25.47.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And his shadow.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:42.48.0:38:43.82.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..So. Michael.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:45.35.0:38:47.22.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Surgeries. Have you had any surgeries
Dialogue: 0.0:38:47.29.0:38:49.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- in the past five years?  - Mm-mm.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:51.63.0:38:54.06.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What about medications? Are you taking any?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:54.13.0:38:55.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. ma'am.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:55.97.0:38:57.87.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Just Benoquin cream for my vitiligo.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:59.20.0:39:00.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:00.97.0:39:03.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You know. it's much more common than people think.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:04.37.0:39:05.81.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Has it spread?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:06.68.0:39:08.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- A little bit.  - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:08.14.0:39:10.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. But. you know. the cream.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:10.18.0:39:12.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..it helps even out my skin tone.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:12.11.0:39:13.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. I see. yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:13.65.0:39:15.92.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Michael. good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:15.99.0:39:17.55.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Almost ready for you. Any. uh...
Dialogue: 0.0:39:17.62.0:39:18.75.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Any last questions?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:18.82.0:39:20.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. no. I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:20.39.0:39:22.83.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..All right. I need to make a few marks around the nose.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:26.63.0:39:29.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You know. you're a pretty good-looking kid.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:29.33.0:39:30.43.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You sure you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:30.50.0:39:33.60.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm not a kid anymore.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:33.67.0:39:35.81.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And my nose is... It's too big.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:35.87.0:39:39.01.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hmm. I'm not sure that's true.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:39.08.0:39:41.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. you see. my face isn't symmetrical
Dialogue: 0.0:39:41.58.0:39:43.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..for the photographs and all.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:44.71.0:39:46.78.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I have to be perfect.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:46.85.0:39:48.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. you're the boss.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:49.15.0:39:50.15.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Just relax.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:25.96.0:40:27.06.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hey!
Dialogue: 0.0:40:28.22.0:40:29.86.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What's going on. son?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:31.73.0:40:32.80.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Son?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:34.96.0:40:36.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Michael?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:40.87.0:40:41.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Boy.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:42.04.0:40:43.24.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..come here.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:52.58.0:40:54.38.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:54.45.0:40:55.65.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What in the world?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:58.62.0:40:59.82.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Let me see something.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:59.89.0:41:00.89.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hey.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:08.83.0:41:10.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. my God.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:12.47.0:41:13.57.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Michael.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:14.80.0:41:16.61.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's for my sinuses.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:48.34.0:41:54.31.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  I guess I'll always be a dreamer  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:41:56.05.0:42:02.28.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Dreaming my life away. dreaming my life away  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:42:04.35.0:42:12.33.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  And nothing comes but sleep. to a dreamer  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:42:12.40.0:42:19.17.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  And when you wake up the dream is gone away  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:42:22.00.0:42:24.01.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Maybe I should get a nose job.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:42:26.71.0:42:28.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- You think so?  - Yes. I do.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:29.98.0:42:31.78.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Muscles says. "Everybody does it."
Dialogue: 0.0:42:31.85.0:42:33.78.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Mm-hmm.  - All the big stars.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:33.85.0:42:36.02.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..All our favorite ones.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:36.09.0:42:37.35.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. it looks great.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:38.59.0:42:40.36.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Do you really think so?  - I do.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:41.99.0:42:44.33.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- See. I wanted a new look.  - Oh. yeah?
Dialogue: 0.0:42:44.39.0:42:46.96.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Reinvent myself.  - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:47.03.0:42:49.60.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You know. now that I'm doing my own thing and...
Dialogue: 0.0:42:51.20.0:42:53.10.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I want the world to see me differently.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:54.34.0:42:56.67.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Not a boy in a kid band anymore.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:57.51.0:42:58.94.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:59.01.0:43:01.61.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Look around. Michael. your fans love you.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:03.38.0:43:04.95.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..They're not my fans.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:05.01.0:43:06.75.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..They're part of my family.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:08.38.0:43:11.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's just time for me to start
Dialogue: 0.0:43:11.35.0:43:12.99.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..taking control of my own destiny.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:13.06.0:43:14.12.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:15.09.0:43:16.19.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You know?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:16.26.0:43:17.86.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I want to be who I want to be.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:19.23.0:43:21.86.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Mikey. Joseph just called a meeting.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:23.70.0:43:25.20.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Careful. he's hungry.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:25.27.0:43:26.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..How hungry?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:26.77.0:43:29.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..He's pretty hungry.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:30.27.0:43:31.81.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..For. like. a mouse?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:31.87.0:43:33.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Maybe.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:36.25.0:43:38.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}There he is! Man of the hour!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:43:38.15.0:43:39.78.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Man of the hour.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:41.78.0:43:43.42.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Come on. sit down. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:47.96.0:43:50.19.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Ah. Now...
Dialogue: 0.0:43:50.26.0:43:52.26.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..you all real happy about Michael's success.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:53.00.0:43:54.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..That's lovely to see.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:54.76.0:43:56.10.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's heartwarming.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:56.17.0:43:57.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I mean. he can go all the way.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:57.97.0:43:58.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Right to the top.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:59.74.0:44:00.94.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..All by himself.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:02.00.0:44:03.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Wouldn't that be something?
Dialogue: 0.0:44:03.41.0:44:05.91.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. man. Let me tell you.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:05.98.0:44:07.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..The Jackson family...
Dialogue: 0.0:44:08.34.0:44:10.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..is the brand.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:10.15.0:44:12.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..That's our Coca-Cola.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:12.25.0:44:14.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. So we need to
Dialogue: 0.0:44:14.25.0:44:17.19.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..open up the store and start selling!
Dialogue: 0.0:44:17.25.0:44:18.85.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Or you know what's gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0.0:44:18.92.0:44:21.59.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Folks are gonna go out there and start buying some Pepsi!
Dialogue: 0.0:44:22.96.0:44:25.46.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..We got to get in there again and vend the wares.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:26.50.0:44:28.63.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..So. I've decided...
Dialogue: 0.0:44:31.64.0:44:33.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm arranging a tour
Dialogue: 0.0:44:33.97.0:44:35.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and a live album.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:37.87.0:44:40.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Wait. how are we gonna tour without Jermaine?
Dialogue: 0.0:44:40.21.0:44:41.38.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Your brother made his choice
Dialogue: 0.0:44:41.44.0:44:43.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..when we left Motown. and he stayed.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:43.55.0:44:44.91.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Let him live with it.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:44.98.0:44:49.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..The point is. we need to capitalize on Michael's album.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:49.12.0:44:51.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..So. we gonna do a bunch of songs--
Dialogue: 0.0:44:51.12.0:44:52.19.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Joseph. I...
Dialogue: 0.0:44:54.16.0:44:56.59.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I... I need to think.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:56.66.0:44:57.76.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. sir.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:57.83.0:44:59.56.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I told you what to think.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:01.33.0:45:02.57.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You got a problem with that. Michael?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:02.63.0:45:04.33.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..We need to have a reasonable conversation
Dialogue: 0.0:45:04.40.0:45:06.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..about this. Joseph.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:06.14.0:45:07.40.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You think now because you're a big
Dialogue: 0.0:45:07.47.0:45:08.77.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..superstar and you have this big hit album
Dialogue: 0.0:45:08.84.0:45:10.84.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..that you're better than everybody in this house?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:10.91.0:45:12.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Is that it?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:12.17.0:45:13.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You better than your brothers?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:14.41.0:45:15.65.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Your mother and me?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:16.35.0:45:17.41.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Is that it?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:18.05.0:45:19.55.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You need to think.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:21.69.0:45:22.95.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You think you're better than me. boy?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:23.02.0:45:24.59.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Joseph. that is enough.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:24.65.0:45:27.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Is that it. Michael? Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:27.36.0:45:28.66.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Is that it?  - That is enough!
Dialogue: 0.0:45:30.26.0:45:31.53.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Katherine. sit down.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:37.77.0:45:38.87.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Let's go.
