Dialogue: 0.0:45:51.58.0:45:52.68.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:53.35.0:45:54.95.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Just drive.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:56.09.0:45:58.52.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay.
