Dialogue: 0.0:46:56.61.0:46:59.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}I'm so sick of it. Bill. All of it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:46:59.15.0:47:01.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Joseph's exploiting me.
