Dialogue: 0.0:47:26.84.0:47:28.21.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You can move out.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:30.18.0:47:31.61.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm not ready for that.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:36.19.0:47:37.65.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's not that easy.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:37.72.0:47:40.82.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Life's not easy. son. I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:47.16.0:47:48.80.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I love my family.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:50.73.0:47:51.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I do.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:55.34.0:47:59.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I just want to do my own thing.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:59.21.0:48:01.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Joseph's never gonna change.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:01.54.0:48:05.68.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Only thing he cares about is the Jackson family. Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:48:05.75.0:48:07.52.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And no matter what you do.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:07.58.0:48:10.75.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..he's only ever gonna see it as a family success.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:11.52.0:48:13.22.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Get your own team.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:14.02.0:48:15.42.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Get you a good lawyer.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:16.06.0:48:17.66.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Think about it.
