Dialogue: 0.0:48:36.35.0:48:39.85.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Looking for  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:48:39.92.0:48:45.15.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  With a friend to call my own  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:48:45.22.0:48:48.53.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  I'll never be alone  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:48:48.59.0:48:52.56.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  And you. my friend. will see  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:48:52.63.0:48:55.80.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  You've got a friend in me  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:49:02.04.0:49:05.81.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Ben. you're always running  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:49:05.88.0:49:09.41.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  Here and there  ♫{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:49:09.48.0:49:13.35.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H6699ff&\i1}♫  You feel you're not wanted  ♫{\i0}
