Dialogue: 0.0:49:59.03.0:50:01.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..So. we appreciate you coming in
Dialogue: 0.0:50:01.76.0:50:05.20.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and we applaud your decision to seek independent counsel.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:05.27.0:50:07.60.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..We can assure you the most comprehensive attention
Dialogue: 0.0:50:07.67.0:50:10.04.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..to your entire media portfolio.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:10.11.0:50:11.61.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..At Hardee Barovick. we believe
Dialogue: 0.0:50:11.67.0:50:13.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..in treating our clients as family
Dialogue: 0.0:50:13.18.0:50:15.85.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- and we want you to--  - I already have a family.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:16.85.0:50:18.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Too much of one.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:20.48.0:50:23.19.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I mean. the whole point's going solo. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:50:23.25.0:50:24.99.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..So. that means you're probably gonna
Dialogue: 0.0:50:25.05.0:50:27.16.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..break a few hearts over there in Encino.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:31.06.0:50:32.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Unless I'm missing something.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:40.40.0:50:41.57.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Do I know you?
Dialogue: 0.0:50:41.64.0:50:43.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:43.81.0:50:45.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You sure?
Dialogue: 0.0:50:45.58.0:50:47.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. I think I'd remember.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:48.88.0:50:50.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Who are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:50:50.81.0:50:52.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..John Branca.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:53.58.0:50:54.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You handle The Beach Boys.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:55.05.0:50:56.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. I do.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:56.39.0:50:58.35.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Neil Diamond. Bob Dylan. couple other guys.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:58.42.0:50:59.66.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and now I work here.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:01.02.0:51:02.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I like The Beach Boys.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:02.36.0:51:03.43.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Me too.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:03.49.0:51:05.03.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Brian Wilson's a genius.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:05.09.0:51:07.10.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Some of the best harmonies in rock and roll.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:11.40.0:51:13.44.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Do you know what I'm after. Mr. Branca?
Dialogue: 0.0:51:13.50.0:51:15.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Sure.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:15.57.0:51:17.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You want to be the biggest star in the world.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:21.61.0:51:23.28.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Can you help make that happen?
Dialogue: 0.0:51:24.41.0:51:25.52.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:26.92.0:51:28.22.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..How?
Dialogue: 0.0:51:29.42.0:51:32.69.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Because I believe there's no one like you.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:34.42.0:51:35.86.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And there never will be.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:44.53.0:51:45.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Mr. Jackson...
Dialogue: 0.0:51:47.64.0:51:50.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Mr. Jackson. I apologize--  - He's my guy.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:55.11.0:51:56.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Can you leave us alone for a second?
Dialogue: 0.0:51:57.98.0:51:59.21.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Please.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:59.75.0:52:00.92.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Of course.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:01.45.0:52:02.79.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:15.43.0:52:17.03.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay. Mr. Branca.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:17.10.0:52:20.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Here's your first job.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:22.27.0:52:23.91.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I need you to fire Joseph.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:26.61.0:52:28.28.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Your dad?
Dialogue: 0.0:52:28.34.0:52:29.78.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You want me to fire your dad?
Dialogue: 0.0:52:31.15.0:52:33.15.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And how would you like me to do that?
Dialogue: 0.0:52:34.12.0:52:35.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Quickly.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:03.18.0:53:04.95.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Yes.  - I think it goes...
Dialogue: 0.0:53:05.01.0:53:06.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Button it up like this.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:06.31.0:53:07.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Right.  - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:07.38.0:53:09.82.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..La Toya. get the hell on out of here.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:11.29.0:53:13.62.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Kate. look at this.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:13.69.0:53:14.79.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Will you look at this?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:14.86.0:53:18.23.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..The boy fired me with a piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:18.29.0:53:20.13.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..A piece of paper. Couldn't even be man to man. huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:20.20.0:53:22.30.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Look me in the eye and do it.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:22.36.0:53:24.40.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..That boy's gonna feel my belt when he get in here!
Dialogue: 0.0:53:26.14.0:53:27.20.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. he's not.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:28.17.0:53:29.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yes. the hell he is.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:29.34.0:53:31.01.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No. he's not.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:31.07.0:53:33.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What are you gonna do. beat him?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:33.18.0:53:34.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You're gonna whoop him?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:35.41.0:53:36.65.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..He's grown.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:36.71.0:53:37.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What'd you say to me?
Dialogue: 0.0:53:41.15.0:53:43.09.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I said you can't do it no more.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:44.59.0:53:45.99.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You can't whoop nobody.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:47.69.0:53:49.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You can't beat nobody.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:51.66.0:53:53.86.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And if you don't like it. you can leave.
Dialogue: 0.0:53:59.33.0:54:00.94.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And the next time you see your son.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:01.00.0:54:02.84.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..you ought to thank him.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:02.91.0:54:05.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Everything we have is because of him
Dialogue: 0.0:54:05.21.0:54:06.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and don't you ever forget that.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:06.78.0:54:08.81.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Everybody seems to forget
Dialogue: 0.0:54:08.88.0:54:10.88.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..that I'm the one that got us out of Gary.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:12.78.0:54:15.02.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And everything I've done
Dialogue: 0.0:54:15.85.0:54:18.02.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..is for this family.
Dialogue: 0.0:54:18.09.0:54:20.46.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You go on ahead and keep thinking that.
