Dialogue: 0.0:55:27.16.0:55:31.36.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'd love an autograph. For my son. I mean.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:31.43.0:55:33.23.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Of course. yeah. Um...
Dialogue: 0.0:55:33.30.0:55:35.13.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..He's a huge fan.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:35.80.0:55:36.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Here.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:36.97.0:55:39.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..How about I sign this? What's your name?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:39.14.0:55:42.31.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Uh. you can just make it out to Pauline.
