Dialogue: 0.0:55:45.21.0:55:47.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Mom. my name's Max. not Pauline.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:47.18.0:55:48.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm not Pauline.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:48.64.0:55:50.28.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Is that the new Atari game?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:51.28.0:55:52.75.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- I love that.  - You've played it?
Dialogue: 0.0:55:52.82.0:55:55.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. yeah. all the time.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:55.38.0:55:58.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Just be sure to keep toggling left when you fire.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:58.12.0:55:59.26.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..That's how you power up.
Dialogue: 0.0:55:59.32.0:56:01.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Cool. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:01.39.0:56:02.49.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Of course.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:03.33.0:56:04.56.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hi.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:04.63.0:56:06.93.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Would you like an autograph?  - Yes. please.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:07.00.0:56:08.93.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- What's your name?  - Monica.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:09.00.0:56:10.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Monica. That's a pretty name.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:10.97.0:56:11.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What do you say. baby?
Dialogue: 0.0:56:12.03.0:56:13.17.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:13.24.0:56:14.67.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..We're huge fans. Michael.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:14.74.0:56:16.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:19.81.0:56:22.41.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Thanks.  - Hey. everybody. Too cute.
