Dialogue: 0.0:56:35.32.0:56:36.49.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What's up. Mikey?
Dialogue: 0.0:56:36.56.0:56:38.43.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- All right. jokers.  - What's up. Bill?
Dialogue: 0.0:56:40.10.0:56:41.16.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Too short.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:44.17.0:56:45.23.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Guys. look!
Dialogue: 0.0:56:45.77.0:56:46.84.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I got {\c&H38d832&\i1}Twister.{\i0}
