Dialogue: 0.0:56:51.17.0:56:52.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Come on. It'll be like the old days.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:53.04.0:56:54.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Would love to. Mike. but I got to be home
Dialogue: 0.0:56:54.54.0:56:55.95.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..with the family. I can't be playing games.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:56.01.0:56:57.95.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And the rest of us are going out tonight.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:58.01.0:56:59.62.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. Marlon's got a hot date.
Dialogue: 0.0:56:59.68.0:57:00.78.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:00.85.0:57:02.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Marlon. what time are you gonna be home?
Dialogue: 0.0:57:02.12.0:57:03.52.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..We could play then.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:03.59.0:57:05.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hey. Marlon's gonna be playing his own game of {\c&H38d832&\i1}Twister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:57:05.32.0:57:06.69.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Shut up. Jackie.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:06.76.0:57:08.56.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm always lucky.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:08.62.0:57:10.39.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. right.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:10.46.0:57:12.46.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- You guys are no fun anymore.  - Come on. Mikey.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:12.53.0:57:13.73.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:17.20.0:57:18.63.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hey. that's cheating.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:18.70.0:57:21.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You got red. not green.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:25.81.0:57:27.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:27.21.0:57:28.64.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:28.71.0:57:30.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It takes a long time to learn
Dialogue: 0.0:57:30.78.0:57:33.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and I'm a professional dancer.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:34.88.0:57:35.95.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You want some ice cream?
Dialogue: 0.0:57:37.25.0:57:38.96.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay. but then I've got to go to work.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:39.72.0:57:40.92.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Don't break anything.
Dialogue: 0.0:57:41.62.0:57:43.76.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'll be back.
