Dialogue: 0.0:59:48.05.0:59:49.29.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Charlie Chaplin.
Dialogue: 0.0:59:50.72.0:59:51.89.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You know who he is?
Dialogue: 0.0:59:52.86.0:59:54.76.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Duh.  - No. you don't.
Dialogue: 0.0:59:55.59.0:59:56.89.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You're such a doo-doo head.
Dialogue: 0.0:59:58.13.1:00:00.23.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..He's wonderful. really.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:00.30.1:00:03.20.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..He's an actor. he's a movie director...
Dialogue: 0.1:00:04.07.1:00:05.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and he writes songs.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:07.97.1:00:09.81.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I have a dog.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:09.87.1:00:11.71.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's a dachshund.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:11.77.1:00:14.41.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Mm. What's his name?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:14.48.1:00:15.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Rudy.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:16.38.1:00:17.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..He's getting fat.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:17.55.1:00:19.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..My mom says I feed him too much.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:20.05.1:00:22.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I love Rudy.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:22.32.1:00:24.15.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Do you have any pets?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:25.05.1:00:28.02.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Uh... A snake
Dialogue: 0.1:00:28.09.1:00:29.53.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and a giraffe.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:29.59.1:00:30.83.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No way.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:30.89.1:00:32.09.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And a llama.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:35.16.1:00:37.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And three parrots. two spiders.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:37.97.1:00:40.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and a whole lot of dogs.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:43.67.1:00:44.74.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's got to be
Dialogue: 0.1:00:44.81.1:00:46.31.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..the greatest-selling album of all time.
