Dialogue: 0.1:00:49.68.1:00:52.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..but by any race. any color. okay?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:52.65.1:00:55.75.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Then I want the largest concert tour there ever was.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:55.82.1:00:57.35.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Just stadiums only.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:57.42.1:00:58.89.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Just thousands and thousands of people
