Dialogue: 0.1:01:26.72.1:01:27.82.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You see...
Dialogue: 0.1:01:28.85.1:01:30.49.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I want to be mysterious.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:31.15.1:01:32.22.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Like-- Like Garbo.
Dialogue: 0.1:01:33.12.1:01:34.32.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You know. but. uh...
Dialogue: 0.1:01:34.39.1:01:36.93.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I mean. if Halley's Comet came every year.
