Dialogue: 0.1:33:20.43.1:33:22.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..is by getting back on that stage.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:23.37.1:33:25.00.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..That's where he lives.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:25.07.1:33:26.67.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I understand that. sir.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:26.74.1:33:28.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- But it's gonna be a while.  - Do you? All right.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:28.17.1:33:31.01.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yes. I do. But. Mr. Jackson...
Dialogue: 0.1:33:31.08.1:33:33.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..he's gonna need your support to get there.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:33.64.1:33:35.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:41.72.1:33:44.42.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's unlikely that will grow back.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:44.49.1:33:47.63.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You'll need surgery to laser the scar tissue
Dialogue: 0.1:33:47.69.1:33:51.33.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and stretch part of the scalp over the burn.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:51.40.1:33:54.67.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..All right? We'll insert an implant to protect the scalp.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:54.73.1:33:56.57.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Will I have to wear a wig?
Dialogue: 0.1:33:56.63.1:33:58.14.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. right there on top.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:00.57.1:34:02.94.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What kind of wig? Like. a full wig?
Dialogue: 0.1:34:03.01.1:34:04.27.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Hard to say.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:04.34.1:34:06.61.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..There are prosthetic hair weaves we can try.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:06.68.1:34:08.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..but we won't know until we see
Dialogue: 0.1:34:08.18.1:34:10.68.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..how the surgery goes next week.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:10.75.1:34:13.15.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Michael! Michael! Michael!
Dialogue: 0.1:34:18.09.1:34:20.22.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You'll. um...
Dialogue: 0.1:34:20.29.1:34:22.43.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You'll have to stay on the Demerol for a while.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:22.49.1:34:24.90.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I don't want to take medication.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:24.96.1:34:26.40.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I have to be honest. Mr. Jackson.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:26.46.1:34:28.60.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..you're gonna need them.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:28.67.1:34:30.93.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..We have to replace the implant periodically.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:31.00.1:34:33.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..The nerves are exposed up there.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:33.14.1:34:34.84.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You'll be in a lot of pain.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:37.71.1:34:40.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'll let you rest. but I'll be back later.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:43.71.1:34:47.15.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Michael! Michael! Michael!
Dialogue: 0.1:34:48.79.1:34:50.16.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You see the number of people
Dialogue: 0.1:34:50.22.1:34:52.46.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..who have already gathered outside the hospital.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:52.52.1:34:54.06.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..If that isn't a testament
Dialogue: 0.1:34:54.13.1:34:55.59.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..to the star power of Michael Jackson.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:55.66.1:34:56.79.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I don't know what is.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:56.86.1:34:57.96.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..The fans say they won't go back
Dialogue: 0.1:34:58.03.1:34:59.96.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..until Michael Jackson's all right.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:02.13.1:35:03.57.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..All right.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:03.63.1:35:05.60.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..All right. Joker.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:05.67.1:35:07.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Got all your favorites.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:07.17.1:35:08.94.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Golden Temple. they send their love.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:09.01.1:35:10.11.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Got some Mexican.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:10.18.1:35:11.18.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Golden Temple's your favorite. Michael.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:11.24.1:35:12.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Chinese. Some fried chicken.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:12.54.1:35:14.41.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Even got these little red candies you like.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:15.98.1:35:19.52.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Thanks. Bill. You can just leave it there.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:19.58.1:35:20.82.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:21.69.1:35:23.19.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. Okay.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:26.89.1:35:28.33.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'll leave you all to it.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:28.39.1:35:31.03.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Okay. Thank you. Bill.  - Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0.1:35:58.96.1:36:00.39.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm sorry. Michael.
Dialogue: 0.1:36:04.73.1:36:06.53.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I should have protected you.
Dialogue: 0.1:36:08.13.1:36:11.64.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Mother. I don't want to discuss this right now.
Dialogue: 0.1:36:12.90.1:36:13.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay.
Dialogue: 0.1:36:20.74.1:36:22.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No one can stop Joseph.
Dialogue: 0.1:36:25.92.1:36:26.98.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Nobody.
Dialogue: 0.1:36:35.73.1:36:38.26.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You just know that. no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0.1:36:39.13.1:36:41.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm gonna be here for you...
Dialogue: 0.1:36:42.07.1:36:43.57.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..always.
Dialogue: 0.1:36:46.80.1:36:48.17.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I should get some rest now. Mother.
Dialogue: 0.1:37:12.70.1:37:14.33.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0.1:37:36.99.1:37:39.36.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..We all need you. Michael!
Dialogue: 0.1:38:15.03.1:38:16.39.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0.1:38:17.03.1:38:18.33.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:18.40.1:38:21.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You know. I'm still in a lot of pain.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:22.20.1:38:24.50.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..But the doctors say I'm healing. So...
Dialogue: 0.1:38:24.57.1:38:25.74.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. that's good news.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:26.67.1:38:28.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..All these kids here...
Dialogue: 0.1:38:29.71.1:38:31.01.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..They won't fully heal
Dialogue: 0.1:38:31.08.1:38:33.41.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and there's burns all over their bodies.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:34.18.1:38:35.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It just breaks my heart.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:36.55.1:38:37.85.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It truly does.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:40.32.1:38:42.02.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You know. it got me thinking...
Dialogue: 0.1:38:43.79.1:38:46.49.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I need to do more for them.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:46.56.1:38:48.79.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..How much are we getting for the accident.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:48.86.1:38:51.46.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..It should be around seven figures.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:51.53.1:38:54.37.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I need every penny donated to the burn center here.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:55.60.1:38:57.70.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Please. you got to make that happen.
Dialogue: 0.1:38:57.77.1:38:58.80.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. of course.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:02.11.1:39:03.81.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm getting really sleepy.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:05.81.1:39:07.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..These pain meds.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:10.65.1:39:11.68.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You get some rest
Dialogue: 0.1:39:11.75.1:39:13.72.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..and I'll come check on you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:14.99.1:39:15.99.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Okay.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:18.62.1:39:20.09.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Did you bring that?
Dialogue: 0.1:39:20.16.1:39:22.79.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Oh. the mouse. yeah. That's from me.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:23.96.1:39:25.50.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- I love that.  - Good.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:26.76.1:39:27.76.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Thank you. Branca.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:27.83.1:39:29.10.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- I'll see you tomorrow.  - See you.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:31.07.1:39:33.24.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}If that boy doesn't go on tour.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:39:34.14.1:39:36.34.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..everything we have falls apart.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:36.41.1:39:40.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm talking deals. sponsorships. our reputation.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:40.58.1:39:42.28.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Everything. Everything just gone.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:42.35.1:39:43.68.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Everything here.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:45.15.1:39:47.75.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..The boys won't be able to tour anymore.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:47.82.1:39:49.59.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Not without Michael.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:49.65.1:39:52.16.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Your son just got out of ICU.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:55.23.1:39:56.56.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Michael never wanted to do
Dialogue: 0.1:39:56.63.1:39:57.93.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..The Victory Tour to begin with.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:58.00.1:40:00.63.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You planned this entire thing behind his back.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:12.44.1:40:15.38.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..When are you gonna realize he's on his own path?
Dialogue: 0.1:40:18.22.1:40:20.65.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..And sometimes. you need to get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:24.29.1:40:26.19.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Otherwise. you're gonna lose him.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:29.49.1:40:31.13.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What about the other boys?
Dialogue: 0.1:40:32.20.1:40:34.03.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..They'll find their own path.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:50.15.1:40:51.58.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}You know something. Bill?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:40:51.65.1:40:53.02.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..What's that?
Dialogue: 0.1:40:53.08.1:40:54.79.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..God's been very good to me.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:54.85.1:40:56.69.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..That he has.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:57.82.1:40:59.96.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Not just the accident.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:00.02.1:41:02.43.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You know. I... I almost died...
Dialogue: 0.1:41:04.06.1:41:05.83.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..but I was given a second chance.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:06.86.1:41:08.07.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. well...
Dialogue: 0.1:41:09.10.1:41:10.60.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..God gave you a gift. son.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:12.04.1:41:13.44.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..A platform...
Dialogue: 0.1:41:14.54.1:41:16.37.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..to reach the whole world.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:18.08.1:41:19.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I can't ignore that.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:22.11.1:41:23.21.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:26.22.1:41:28.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I have to shine my light.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:28.95.1:41:31.22.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Spread love and joy.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:32.89.1:41:34.09.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..To heal.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:39.40.1:41:40.43.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:43.13.1:41:44.57.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..That's my destiny.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:46.77.1:41:48.91.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I truly believe that.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:48.97.1:41:51.74.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Well. why don't we focus on getting you healthy first?
Dialogue: 0.1:41:51.81.1:41:53.88.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Then we can do all those things you need to do.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:53.94.1:41:55.05.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm gonna do the tour.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:56.55.1:41:57.61.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0.1:41:58.45.1:41:59.65.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..For my family.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:01.75.1:42:03.25.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..But then I'm ready. Bill.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:08.46.1:42:10.26.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I'm gonna look him straight in the eye.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:11.06.1:42:12.46.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..This is my life.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:15.57.1:42:16.77.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..My path.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:21.47.1:42:22.51.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Mine.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:44.96.1:42:46.80.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Okay. let's go out there and tear that stage up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:42:46.86.1:42:48.13.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Yeah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:42:48.20.1:42:49.30.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Give the audience what they deserve.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:42:49.37.1:42:50.97.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Yeah.  - The best show ever.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:52.10.1:42:53.80.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}I told you what to think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:42:54.97.1:42:56.64.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..I love you guys.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:56.71.1:42:58.41.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}You ain't like everyone else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:42:58.48.1:43:00.21.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}You think you're better than me. boy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:43:00.28.1:43:01.88.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..- Love you. too. Mike.  - I really do.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:01.95.1:43:03.81.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Love you. too. Mike.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:03.88.1:43:05.48.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}Nobody else will understand you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:43:05.55.1:43:07.72.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}outside this place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:43:07.78.1:43:11.42.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..The Jacksons on three. One. two. three...
Dialogue: 0.1:43:11.49.1:43:12.49.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Jacksons!
Dialogue: 0.1:43:14.19.1:43:16.26.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}After I give these boys a rest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:43:16.33.1:43:18.30.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}I'm planning an international tour.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:43:18.36.1:43:19.73.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..{\c&H38d832&\i1}With Michael?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:43:19.80.1:43:23.17.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. we're gonna hit all the big arenas and stadiums.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:23.23.1:43:25.57.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..This is just the beginning of The Victory Tour.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:25.64.1:43:26.80.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..You got more shows?
Dialogue: 0.1:43:26.87.1:43:29.17.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Yeah. we gonna hit every continent.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:29.24.1:43:32.44.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..But. first of all. we're going to Paris. London. Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:32.51.1:43:35.08.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..South Africa. You name it. we gonna be there.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:35.15.1:43:38.02.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..This is gonna be the biggest anyone has ever seen.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:45.99.1:43:47.16.1.85:1 BS..0.0.0..Shh! Shh!
